# Klyria Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** October 2025  

---

## 1. Overview
Klyria is a privacy-first clipboard manager designed to help you securely save, search, and organize your copied text and images ‚Äî all directly on your device.  
We do **not** collect, sell, or share any personal information. Your clipboard history and preferences remain entirely private to you.

---

## 2. Data We Do Not Collect
- ‚ùå We do **not** collect your name, email address, Apple ID, or any personal identifiers.  
- ‚ùå We do **not** track your usage, behavior, or clipboard content.  
- ‚ùå We do **not** serve ads or share data with third parties.

---

## 3. Data Stored on Your Device
All clipboard data, preferences, and settings are stored **locally on your iPhone or iPad**.  
If you delete the app, all stored clips and data are permanently erased.

---

## 4. iCloud Sync (Pro Feature)
If you enable **iCloud Sync**, your clips are securely stored in your private iCloud account using **Apple‚Äôs CloudKit** framework.  

- Your data is **end-to-end encrypted** and isolated from other users.  
- Klyria **cannot access** or view your synced data ‚Äî only you can.  
- This data counts toward your personal iCloud storage quota, not Klyria‚Äôs.  

You can disable iCloud Sync at any time in the app‚Äôs settings.

---

## 5. Face ID / Touch ID
Klyria may use biometric authentication (Face ID or Touch ID) to lock or unlock access to your saved clips.  
This authentication occurs **entirely on your device** via Apple‚Äôs Secure Enclave.  
We do **not** collect or store any biometric information.

---

## 6. In-App Purchases
Klyria offers optional in-app purchases (subscriptions or lifetime unlock).  
All transactions are processed securely through **Apple‚Äôs App Store**.  
Klyria does not collect, store, or process any payment information.

---

## 7. App Extensions
Klyria includes optional extensions such as:
- **Share Sheet Extension** ‚Äî to save clips from Safari, Photos, and other apps.  
- **Custom Keyboard** ‚Äî to paste clips conveniently into any app.  

These extensions only access the content you explicitly choose to share at the moment of use.

---

## 8. Children‚Äôs Privacy
Klyria is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect information from children under 13.

